{"tid":2415364,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺誠哥兩個仔其實幾撚屈","createTime":"2021-02-20T07:44:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-20T08:35:39.000Z","uid":90615,"like":6,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"bf021e649ed2258fc690905e488fad71041796c8","tid":2415364,"uid":90615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T07:44:10.000Z","msg":"出名有錢人二代黎講基本上得佢兩個真係掂<br />\n大佬玩過全盛期isabella 生左兩粒身家都唔洗分<br />\n自己又搞個pccw出黎<br />\n細佬低調啲但都叫hold到盤數（利申唔撚知）<br />\n<br />\n何家二代後生個班一個衰過一個<br />\n又神童又盛結果娶隻大陸雞<br />\n<br />\n大劉個仔真心膠 接個海洋公園返黎做到on9咁<br />\n<br />\n鍾培生典型二（三）世祖一件 連搞死個打機發跡既mk仔toyz都搞唔掂<br />\n<br />\n再下面唔入流個啲仲有隻柒頭林作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點解誠哥咁識教仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fd0c351b7a48a41a597620edef3924e6411db84","tid":2415364,"uid":119695,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T07:44:56.000Z","msg":"你係咪搞錯咗大佬同細佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc7c2adbcc009bb4c88246aa6b79b9a9c3b0f74b","tid":2415364,"uid":103237,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T07:44:59.000Z","msg":"細佬同大佬你都分唔清"},{"pid":"15a1dd36bb4b63bf92f4eaf44e1b65dd5d1295d6","tid":2415364,"uid":166729,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T07:45:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇完頭兩句, 此post已完"},{"pid":"c8959cdc4b13163fada84259ada2dbd86b6c03ab","tid":2415364,"uid":293783,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T07:45:35.000Z","msg":"大細佬掉轉左"},{"pid":"e481f426bb84bbd744ef393bb8dc51949073f1aa","tid":2415364,"uid":90615,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"quote":{"pid":"1fd0c351b7a48a41a597620edef3924e6411db84","tid":2415364,"uid":119695,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T07:44:56.000Z","msg":"你係咪搞錯咗大佬同細佬